Turn on airplane mode and turn off Wifi 开启飞行模式并关闭Wifi
Open Phone Manager > App Launcher Management> Four Dout > Show System Apps  App Launcher Management > Search Google  Change Google's four-piece set to manual management,and turn on all three switches 打开手机管家>应用启动管理>四个点>显示系统应用   应用启动管理>搜索Google 将Google四件套改成手动管理，三个开关都开
First clear up the data of Google Servise Framework and then stop running it 先把Google服务框架的数据清理掉，然后停止运行
Then clear the cache of Google Play Services and stop running it 再把Google Play服务的缓存清理掉，然后停止运行
Finally,clear the data of Google Play Store and stpo running it 最后把Google Play商店的数据清理掉，然后停止运行
Restart your device 重启设备
After restarting the device,clear the data of Google Play Services(Storage > Manage Space > Clear All Data at the bottom)and stop running 重启设备后，清除Gooogle Play服务的数据（储存>管理空间>最下面的清楚所有数据）并停止运行
Restart the device again 再次重启设备
After restartingthe device,turn off airplane mode and turn on Wifi 重启设备后，关闭飞行模式，打开Wifi
Open the Play Store,click on your profile picture > Settings > Auto-update apps Change Auto-update to Do not auto-update apps 打开Play商店，点头像>设置>自动更新应用 自动更新应用改成不自动更新应用
Uninstall Google Play Services 卸载Google Play服务
Download z5service.apk and install 下载z5service.apk并安装
